                            <comment id="10961" author="rread" created="Tue, 8 Mar 2011 11:08:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This will break in the not too distant future when we have alternative disk filesystems. Would it be possible to change the ldiskfs package to provide lustre-backend-fs and the lustre-modules can require that instead?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
